                            <comment id="17051245" author="gnt" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2020 14:02:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The syntax with the &lt;tt&gt;ref&lt;/tt&gt; attribute was deprecated. You should now use&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;marshal&amp;gt;&amp;lt;custom ref=&quot;xstream-default&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/marshal&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And I agree the error is a bit misleading, it can be improved here.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17051294" author="mattias1972" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2020 14:51:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for your help. Worked perfectly. I&apos;ll close this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17051297" author="mattias1972" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2020 14:52:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No bug. Using the right syntax worked perfectly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
